ool and saw my father on the table. He had the nerve destroyed at the back of the ear. To stop him from getting thes}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12993658\charrsid5983795 e light heads and dizziness. Diz}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
