\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid418543 RW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14944617\charrsid5983795 Yes, all the limit, yes.
