Well - well not - not - I wouldn't call - not as important, I don't think. Used to look up to some of them, I mean there was - there was a - a chappie used to have a
 - where they're building these new flats now they - and that used to be - a market garden. And there was a Mr and Mrs Tottie and the sn used to work that and I've heard it said I used to go there as a little boy every Saturday morning and go and get a ro
se off them for my mother. I used to have me course apron on, wrapped round you know, for a - every Saturday morning for a rose for me mother. Yes.
