Well I think they were - it was more or less a community of your own - you - you knew everybody sort of thing then, those days you see because you were - there was only these - there was nothing the other side of here and Ollerton Road was only just in t
he way of making then. And there was no Mather Avenue - there was no Merrill Avenue so far - it was up to Green Lane you see.
